reviewText: A terrible movie. Terrible dialogue if you want to call it that since there was very little of that. I wasn't able to make any sense of it whatsoever.
This movie was written, produced, and directed by people who should re-evaluate their career choice.
Terrible movie, I've given zero Stars if I could
Turned it off 15 minutes in. I usually have patience but this sucked. I suspect those 5 stars came from the makes of the movie, i.e. writer, director, actors.
Really like the look of this movie, and the kid is pretty bad ass too!
